description: Add geospatial and location intelligence functionality to your Android, iOS, and Windows apps with ArcGIS Runtime SDK for .NET. Provides a cross-platform API to access a comprehensive set of mapping and spatial analytics capabilities including: vector tile basemaps; a wide range of standards-based ready-to-use and custom data layers; powerful search and topological operations; optimized routing and navigation; field data collection with offline editing and enterprise synchronization; and utility network tracing.
